contentrichtext.text: '''Integra''' may refer to: * [[Honda Integra]] a compact car * [[Integra Air]], a Canadian airline * [[Integra Bank]], a regional bank headquartered in Evansville, Indiana * [[Integra Hellsing]], a main character of the manga and anime series ''Hellsing'' * [[Integra Home Theater]], a premium audio video components manufacturer * [[Integra Telecom]], a telecommunications company * [[Integra Incorporated]], a computer graphics company * [[Integra Signum]], a (defunct) Swiss railroad signaling company * Integra FLEX, a line of automatic test equipment sold by [[Teradyne]] * Integra and Grand Integra, product lines of aural reproduction and home theatre systems from [[Onkyo]] * [http://www.integra.cl/integra.nsf/data/2F559BC06ADF56BA842577B200619DB0 Integra Foundation] (Chile), the national pre-school network. == See also == * [[Integral (disambiguation)]] {{disambig}}
